{"id":"guide/routing-overview","title":"Angular 路由","contents":"<div class=\"content\">\n  <h1 id=\"angular-routing\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"3pkknx48jl2etpoppg3wqtxhq\">Angular 路由<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/routing-overview#angular-routing\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"exfc3p0ihjsakx4j9ma7w44k\">在單頁應用中，你可以透過顯示或隱藏與特定元件相對應的部分來更改使用者看到的內容，而不用去伺服器獲取新頁面。使用者執行應用程式任務時，他們需要在定義好的不同<a href=\"guide/glossary#view\" title=\"檢視的定義\">檢視</a>之間移動。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7aeauxgiooniiieqqrxk0jqyw\">要處理從一個<a href=\"guide/glossary#view\">檢視</a>到下一個檢視的導向，請使用 Angular <strong><code><a href=\"api/router/Router\" class=\"code-anchor\">Router</a></code></strong>。<strong><code><a href=\"api/router/Router\" class=\"code-anchor\">Router</a></code></strong> 會通過將瀏覽器 URL 解釋為更改檢視的操作指令來啟用導向。</p>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ba467i59ocg238fdk871etaza\">要瀏覽具有主要路由器功能的範例應用，請參閱<live-example name=\"router\"></live-example>。</p>\n<h2 id=\"prerequisites\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e44b21uig1fakj5vcfuvz1bdu\">前提條件<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/routing-overview#prerequisites\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"79lc5jz66u2bj4ro3lw6coo5o\">在建立路由之前，你應該熟悉以下內容：</p>\n<ul>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"f2juqutjpadle5b16ec0pok4o\"><a href=\"guide/architecture-components\">元件基礎</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1basrmrmsgqz0ktslwd53at7b\"><a href=\"guide/glossary#template\">樣板基礎</a></li>\n<li data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4k3kmct4x9h72mltgo0qtu9eu\">一個 Angular 應用程式 - 你可以使用 <a href=\"cli\">Angular CLI</a> 生成基本的 Angular 應用程式。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"learn-about-angular-routing\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"dhgphp4gpi2ca0a6r4xt4yg6h\">瞭解 Angular 路由<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"guide/routing-overview#learn-about-angular-routing\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n<div class=\"card-container\">\n  <a href=\"guide/router\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Common routing tasks\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c7hyyis4p52xcejqj0mhc2f0g\">通用路由任務</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1abufwdzutned62einv5fnzyt\">瞭解如何實現與 Angular 路由相關的許多常見任務。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"c7hyyis4p52xcejqj0mhc2f0g\">通用路由任務</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/router-tutorial\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Routing SPA tutorial\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"7jynfn3d97d0wx0buxwrefhxz\">單頁應用程式 (SPA) 路由教程</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"ajg8e6r2bqul6gfoz2lwmarc1\">一個涵蓋與 Angular 路由相關的模式的教程。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"6vpg5pjkqa6c4guvk3gbqethj\">路由 SPA 教程</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/router-tutorial-toh\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Routing Tour of Heroes\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"4y72qocffmcnp0y9kddrcouv9\">英雄之旅擴充套件路由教程</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"chikecd94atitss0p4qhxok22\">為 Tour of Heroes 教程新增更多路由屬性。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8klx5hy43zcm7lvcrttisvr8j\">英雄路由之旅</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/routing-with-urlmatcher\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Creating custom route matches tutorial\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"70hdix6rw1wjzs45i5lkt2zeg\">建立自定義路由對應教程</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"e05v4gy0p8uhtkmnvrm6y4b1w\">一個教程，介紹如何將自定義對應策略模式與 Angular 路由一起使用。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"1d9bwmrsi6e20csw20va7rl7h\">自定義路由對應教程</p>\n  </a>\n  <a href=\"guide/router-reference\" class=\"docs-card\" title=\"Router reference\">\n    <section data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8nm57pkx5kpvbovblew31w06l\">路由器參考</section>\n    <p data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"eituxk231wt8k0ecu7gi2qq4u\">描述一些核心路由器 API 概念。</p>\n    <p class=\"card-footer\" data-ng_translator_product=\"100\" data-ng_translator_ref_id=\"8nm57pkx5kpvbovblew31w06l\">路由器參考</p>\n  </a>\n</div>\n<!-- links -->\n<!-- external links -->\n<!-- end links -->\n\n  <div class=\"reviewed\">最後複查時間：Mon Feb 28 2022</div>\n</div>\n\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - features\n - guide/developer-guide-overview\n - scaling\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-10\n - tutorial/first-app/first-app-lesson-11\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - api/router/Router\n - cli\n - guide/architecture-components\n - guide/glossary#template\n - guide/glossary#view\n - guide/router\n - guide/router-reference\n - guide/router-tutorial\n - guide/router-tutorial-toh\n - guide/routing-overview#angular-routing\n - guide/routing-overview#learn-about-angular-routing\n - guide/routing-overview#prerequisites\n - guide/routing-with-urlmatcher\n-->"}